<h2 id="executive-agencies">Executive agencies</h2>

<p><abbr title="Department for Education">DfE</abbr>’s media team handles media enquiries on behalf of our executive agencies:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/education-and-skills-funding-agency">Education and Skills Funding Agency (<abbr title="Education and Skills Funding Agency">ESFA</abbr>)</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/teaching-regulation-agency">Teaching Regulation Agency (<abbr title="Teaching Regulation Agency">TRA</abbr>)</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/standards-and-testing-agency">Standards and Testing Agency (<abbr title="Standards and Testing Agency">STA</abbr>)</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="non-departmental-public-bodies">Non-departmental public bodies</h3>

<p>If you have a specific enquiry about a policy that is managed by a non-departmental public body, you should contact the relevant body’s press office.</p>

